    public abstract class AnnotatedServiceLocator
extends java.lang.Object
implements ServiceLocator
    Default Implementation of an ServiceLocator that uses the Pluggable Annotation Processing API (JSR-269) to find Services that are annotated with Service Annotations.

    Philipp Schürmann
